item.title: Little Big Planet (2008): Retro Review
item.description:
Some games make us push ourselves until we want to throw our controllers. Others pit us against each other in PvP combat to see which of our friends is superior.

Then there is a third category of video game that brings everyone together to have a good time, laugh, and forget about everything else... Feed: https://anchor.fm/s/5337b40c/podcast/rss
